thread.title: Jack Clarke

author: Jack Clarke
title: Jack Clarke
text: Love all the merchandise there is always good deathmetal merch, which is sick as I live in the U.K. and the uk sucks for metal clothing, I rely on gigs for most of my metal merch. I have ordered numerious times from impericon, can't fault the service, I have ordered multiple items each time and I'm always pleased with the speedy service. Keep up the good work dudes, lets get Fuking metal!!!
